name: Warhammer Underworlds: Online - Warband: Spiteclaw's Swarm
summary: Seemingly infinite in number, the devious and malicious ratmen known as skaven blight every corner and crevice in the city of Shadespire. Unlock this warband and play as Spiteclaw's Swarm in Warhammer Underworlds: Online.
